1
00:00:00,970 --> 00:00:03,533
Welcome to the McGlynn Elementary School community.

2
00:00:04,053 --> 00:00:06,836
My name is Andy O'Brien and I am your child's principal.

3
00:00:07,677 --> 00:00:17,928
Our staff of over 70 teachers, assistants, paraprofessionals, administrators, and other service providers will work to make your child's educational year productive as well as fun.

4
00:00:18,888 --> 00:00:27,593
The McGlynn offers our 500-plus pre-K through grade 5 students many wonderful opportunities both in and out of our school.

5
00:00:28,453 --> 00:00:33,877
Our learning environment is child-centered and rich with interactive lessons in all curriculum areas.

6
00:00:34,577 --> 00:00:39,860
The McGlynn also services the Access and the Newcomer English Language Learner Program.

7
00:00:41,144 --> 00:00:50,550
Our teachers and staff focus on educating the whole child with meaningful, real-world experiences in a manner that is educational, valuable, and enjoyable.

8
00:00:51,590 --> 00:00:58,595
We are committed to meeting each child's individual needs and ability level, which includes their social and emotional well-being.

9
00:00:59,575 --> 00:01:05,139
We encourage you to get involved and stay involved in your child's education in any way you can.

10
00:01:06,189 --> 00:01:11,752
Please know I will try my best to make your children feel like an individual here at the McGlynn.

11
00:01:12,713 --> 00:01:16,055
Our school and our members are committed to you and your family.

12
00:01:16,655 --> 00:01:18,136
It is important that we work together.

13
00:01:18,816 --> 00:01:22,478
To that end, it is extremely important that you know how to get in touch with us.

14
00:01:23,579 --> 00:01:27,141
The best way to stay informed is to read each monthly newsletter.

15
00:01:27,801 --> 00:01:32,304
These will be emailed to your address on file as well as posted to this website.

16
00:01:33,103 --> 00:01:40,767
The monthly newsletters allow you to stay up to date with everything taking place at the McGlynn and by the active McGlynn PTG.

17
00:01:41,727 --> 00:01:50,891
Also, both the district and school websites include important pieces of information that will enable you to remain in contact and informed all year long.

18
00:01:51,812 --> 00:01:54,413
Be sure to visit these various features often.

19
00:01:55,694 --> 00:01:59,278
Welcome, and I wish you many successes in the years ahead.

20
00:01:59,919 --> 00:02:02,803
Thank you for taking an active interest in your child's learning.

21
00:02:03,283 --> 00:02:07,769
And please remember, all of us at the McGlynn care about your child.

